      "link"			: "http://hywel.github.io/blog/all-long-time-between-posts/",
      "excerpt"		: "<p>It has been a long time since updates and considering the effort I put in to set up this frame work, I thought I should start this up again. I will try to post some articles/tutorials on the new <a href="http://ips-lmu.github.io/EMU.html">Emu Speech Database</a> and my experiences with using it for teaching and research.</p>

